richContent.title: I’m here to help!
text: I understand, it’s completely fine if you don’t want to take any tests. I’m here to listen. How are you feeling right now?
By the way, I can do more than just listen. If you'd like, I can help you:
- Watch your favorite video or song on the internet.
- Recommend relaxing music or mindfulness exercises.
- Even guide you through a quick mental therapy session to help ease your mind.
- I can tell you some lame jokes so you can cuss me :)
- You can tell me about your day and whatever you are feeling:)
- Or you can simply surf whatever you like
Let me know what you'd like to do. I'm here for you.
